  "content": "<h2>更新：新版Ankidroid已经解决了这个问题，本文作废</h2><hr/><h2>问题</h2><p data-pid=\"8a0Ut35t\">一直以来，劝退 anki 新手有三大门槛（现编的，233333）：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"fWonsl3X\">PC——电脑怎么用？</li><li data-pid=\"xOaSVNCc\">安卓——这个 apkg 牌组文件怎么打不开啊？</li><li data-pid=\"1ZGowNVz\">苹果——一个 app 要 163 元，能便宜点吗？</li></ol><p data-pid=\"v8G_1D3i\">虽然写了很多很多教程，但都无法直接解决这个问题，让不少同学从入门到放弃，只花了 5 分钟。</p><h2>解决方案</h2><p data-pid=\"qKe-yLuJ\">于是乎，我改了一下 AnkiDroid 的几行代码，并打包成了 apk 安装包，方便朋友们下载。</p><p data-pid=\"hKdPfX-h\">PS：如果提示已存在较高版本，需要卸载原来安装的 AnkiDroid。</p><p data-pid=\"SR7MvipR\">网盘下载：</p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//pan.baidu.com/s/16JFHGO9Yk1hlUD1d84iCGA%23list/path%3D%252F%26parentPath%3D%252Fsharelink3091266325-210474336702130\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/16JFHGO9Yk1hlUD1d84iCGA</a><p data-pid=\"L448ve89\">源码：</p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/L-M-Sherlock/Anki-Android\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/L-M-Sherlock</span><span class=\"invisible\">/Anki-Android</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><h2>效果</h2><p data-pid=\"lh4Lnh-F\">百度云</p><a class=\"video-box\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/1187432742386737152\" target=\"_blank\" data-video-id=\"\" data-video-playable=\"\" data-name=\"\" data-poster=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c85d69209ce7b7488c0998ba18769007.jpeg\" data-lens-id=\"1187432742386737152\"><img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c85d69209ce7b7488c0998ba18769007.jpeg\"/><span class=\"content\"><span class=\"title\"><span class=\"z-ico-extern-gray\"></span><span class=\"z-ico-extern-blue\"></span></span><span class=\"url\"><span class=\"z-ico-video\"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/1187432742386737152</span></span></a><p data-pid=\"NQH1lWyw\">QQ/TIM</p><a class=\"video-box\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/1187432813333331968\" target=\"_blank\" data-video-id=\"\" data-video-playable=\"\" data-name=\"\" data-poster=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a859aa1fa4b111163214d731f49fb8b8.jpeg\" data-lens-id=\"1187432813333331968\"><img class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a859aa1fa4b111163214d731f49fb8b8.jpeg\"/><span class=\"content\"><span class=\"title\"><span class=\"z-ico-extern-gray\"></span><span class=\"z-ico-extern-blue\"></span></span><span class=\"url\"><span class=\"z-ico-video\"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/1187432813333331968</span></span></a><h2>结语</h2><p data-pid=\"J2NuWFh8\">如果你想把 Anki 安利给朋友，恰好 TA 用的是安卓系统，不妨把本文中的安装包发给 TA，避免导入牌组劝退。</p><p data-pid=\"-TKAJCE5\">当然，别忘了把本专栏也安利给 TA 一下，23333</p>",
